  "description": "Add Translation for \"Open Now\" Status Indicator on English Pages\n\nImplement proper translation handling for the \"Open Now\" status indicator that is currently displaying untranslated text on English language pages.\n\nRequirements:\n- Locate all instances of the \"Open Now\" status indicator in the codebase\n- Ensure the text is wrapped in the translation function/system\n- Add or verify the English translation key exists in the language files\n- Verify the indicator displays correctly translated text on English pages\n- Test that translations work correctly for all supported languages (not just English)\n- Check for any similar untranslated status indicators (e.g., \"Closed\", \"Opening Soon\") that may need the same fix",
